title: War of the Roses: Who's the girl in the bikini on his phone?
description: Megan really has no reason to suspect her boyfriend Jack is cheating besides a picture she found on his phone.  It's not that incriminating of a picture but she still wants to do War of the Roses on Jack to see if it could be something.
